text: Elena Andreyevna Rybakina (born 17 June 1999) is a Russian-born Kazakhstani professional tennis player. She won the Wimbledon Championships in 2022 and she is the first Kazakhstani player to win a major title. She is also the first to be ranked in the world's top 15, with a career-high ranking of No. 12 by the Women's Tennis Association (WTA). Rybakina was born in Moscow, Russia. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Wimbledon champions Category:Russian tennis players Category:Kazakhstani sportspeople Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
